comments: After the offensive rebound and pass, Westbrook (LAL) takes a step towards Murphy III (NOP) and makes marginal contact with him.
Valanciunas (NOP) makes marginal contact with Westbrook (LAL) as moves into him during the screen.
Westbrook (LAL) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Reaves (LAL) legally contests Murphy III's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Monk (LAL) legally contests the shot attempt in the post by Valanciunas (NOP).
Anthony (LAL) leans in and delivers contact to Murphy III (NOP) while setting the screen.
Marshall (NOP) legally contests James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Replay confirmed that James (LAL) touched the ball after it has reached its apex.
Ingram (NOP) legally contests Monk's (LAL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Westbrook (LAL) commits a take foul on Jones (NOP).
